🗄 Database Design (Very Important)
Users Table
users
-----
id
name
phone
email
role (donor/receiver)
location
created_at
Food Posts Table
food_posts
----------
id
user_id (donor)
food_name
quantity
description
expiry_time
location
status (available/requested/completed)
created_at
Requests Table
requests
--------
id
food_id
receiver_id
status (pending/accepted/rejected)
created_at

This is clean relational design 👌

🔐 Important Things to Consider

Because this involves real people:

1️⃣ Safety

Add disclaimer

Donor responsible for food quality

2️⃣ Location privacy

Don’t show exact address until accepted

3️⃣ Food expiry validation

Auto-hide expired food

